      "value": "<p>Your body and soul share a powerful connection that makes you particularly resilient against having your life snuffed out.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Con 13</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Whenever you take damage from the initial onset of a poison or a source that deals negative energy damage, reduce that damage by your Constitution modifier. At 10th level, this reduction becomes equal to twice your Constitution modifier.</p>\n<p>([[/ ternary(gte(@details.level.value, 10), (@abilities.con.mod * 2), (@abilities.con.mod))]])</p>"
